# Puchi Frontend

Puchi là nền tảng web học tiếng Việt. Frontend dùng **Next.js 16 (App Router) + React 19**.

## Tech Stack

| Thành phần | Công nghệ |
|------------|-----------|
| Framework | Next.js 16 (App Router, output: standalone) |
| UI | Tailwind CSS v4 + Shadcn UI (New York) |
| State | Zustand v5 |
| Auth | Supertokens self-host — `supertokens-web-js` (client) + `supertokens-node` (server) |
| i18n | next-intl (9 ngôn ngữ) |
| Animation | Motion + Rive |
| Runtime | Bun (install) + Node.js 22 (build & run) |

## Auth — Supertokens

**Đã migrate từ Clerk → Supertokens hoàn tất.** Không còn Clerk.

### Client-side (`supertokens-web-js`)
```typescript
// src/config/supertokens.ts
SuperTokens.init({
  appInfo: {
    appName: "Puchi",
    apiDomain: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL,  // https://puchi.io.vn (same-origin!)
    apiBasePath: "/api/auth",
  },
  recipeList: [EmailPassword.init(), ThirdParty.init(), Session.init()],
});
```

**Quan trọng**: `apiDomain` = `puchi.io.vn` (cùng origin với website), **không phải** `api.puchi.io.vn`. Supertokens Node SDK cần cùng origin để set cookie đúng cách.

### Server-side (`supertokens-node`)
```typescript
// src/config/supertokens-server.ts
const supertokensConfig = {
  supertokens: {
    connectionURI: process.env.SUPERTOKENS_CONNECTION_URI || "http://localhost:30567",
    apiKey: process.env.SUPERTOKENS_API_KEY,
  },
  appInfo: {
    appName: "Puchi",
    apiDomain: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL,
    websiteDomain: process.env.NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN,
    apiBasePath: "/api/auth",
    websiteBasePath: "/auth",
  },
  recipeList: [
    EmailPasswordNode.init(),
    ThirdPartyNode.init({
      providers: [Google, Facebook, TikTok],
    }),
    SessionNode.init(),
  ],
};
```

### API Route handler
Next.js API route `src/app/api/auth/[...path]/route.ts` xử lý mọi request auth:
- GET/POST/PUT/DELETE/PATCH → `getAppDirRequestHandler()` (từ supertokens-node)
- Request clone để tránh lỗi stream body (formData + json)

### Auth flow tổng thể
```
Browser → supertokens-web-js → /api/auth/[...path] → supertokens-node → st-core-svc:3567
     (puchi.io.vn)         (Next.js API route)
```

## Docker Build

Multi-stage build với Bun + Node.js:

| Stage | Image | Purpose |
|-------|-------|---------|
| deps | `oven/bun:1.2-slim` | Install dependencies (Bun nhanh) |
| builder | `node:22-alpine` | Build Next.js (Node vì Next.js 16 chưa support Bun build) |
| runner | `node:22-alpine` | Run production (non-root user nextjs) |

Build args từ CI/CD:
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` — https://puchi.io.vn
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` — https://api.puchi.io.vn

Output: `standalone` (Next.js output tracing), copy thêm `node_modules` để đảm bảo supertokens-node hoạt động đúng.

## CI/CD

GitHub Actions (`ci-cd.yml`):
- **Lint**: Bun install → ESLint
- **Build & Push**: Docker login GHCR → Build + Push (tag: latest + sha)
- **Build args**: NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN
- **Registry**: `ghcr.io/puchidemy/puchi-frontend`

## Key Env Vars

| Env | Production value | Notes |
|-----|-----------------|-------|
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | App domain, cũng là apiDomain cho supertokens |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` | `https://api.puchi.io.vn` | API gateway (Envoy Gateway) |
| `NEXT_PUBLIC_WEBSITE_DOMAIN` | `https://puchi.io.vn` | Website domain |
| `SUPERTOKENS_CONNECTION_URI` | `http://st-core-svc.puchi-infra.svc.cluster.local:3567` | Supertokens core (dev: localhost:30567) |
| `SUPERTOKENS_API_KEY` | (secret) | API key |
| `GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | (secret) | Google OAuth |
| `FACEBOOK_CLIENT_ID/SECRET` | (secret) | Facebook OAuth |
| `TIKTOK_CLIENT_KEY/SECRET` | (secret) | TikTok OAuth |

## Scripts

```bash
bun install          # Cài dependencies
bun run dev          # Dev server (webpack mode)
bun run build        # Build production (chạy bằng Node.js)
bun run start        # Start production
bun run lint         # ESLint
```

## Cấu trúc thư mục

```
src/
├── app/[locale]/     # Next.js App Router pages (i18n)
├── app/api/auth/     # Supertokens API route handler
├── components/       # UI components (Shadcn + custom)
├── config/           # Supertokens client + server config
├── providers/        # SupertokensProvider (init client-side)
├── lib/              # Utilities, API clients
├── store/            # Zustand stores
├── hooks/            # Custom hooks
├── i18n/             # Translation config
├── services/         # API service layer
├── styles/           # Global styles
├── constants/        # Constants
└── types/            # TypeScript types
```

## Kết nối Backend

- API qua Envoy Gateway tại `api.puchi.io.vn`
- Auth: Supertokens (internal, không expose ra ngoài)
